#: ../../G/Great-Renaming.rst:5
msgid "Great Renaming"
msgstr "Great Renaming"

#: ../../G/Great-Renaming.rst:7
msgid "n\\."
msgstr "名詞"

#: ../../G/Great-Renaming.rst:9
msgid ""
"The :ref:`flag-day` in 1987 on which all of the non-local groups on the "
":ref:`Usenet` had their names changed from the net.- format to the current "
"multiple-hierarchies scheme. Used esp. in discussing the history of "
"newsgroup names. \"The oldest sources group is :code:`comp.sources.misc`\\; "
"before the Great Renaming, it was :code:`net.sources`\\.\" There is a `Great"
" Renaming FAQ <http://www.vrx.net/usenet/history/rename.html>`_\\  on the "
"Web."
msgstr ""
"1987年の\\ :ref:`flag-day`\\ で、この日に\\ :ref:`Usenet`\\ "
"上のすべての非ローカルなグループの名前が、net.-形式から現在の複数階層方式に変更された。特にニュースグループ名の歴史を論じる際に使われる。「最も古いソースグループは\\"
" :code:`comp.sources.misc`\\ である。Great Renamingの前は、それは\\ "
":code:`net.sources`\\ だった。」ウェブ上に `Great Renaming FAQ "
"<http://www.vrx.net/usenet/history/rename.html>`_\\  がある。"
